Flask
selenium
selenium-wire
webdriver-manager

# Create a virtual environment
python -m venv venv

# Activate the virtual environment
# On Windows
venv\Scripts\activate
# On macOS/Linux
source venv/bin/activate

# Install Flask, selenium, selenium-wire, and webdriver-manager
pip install Flask selenium selenium-wire webdriver-manager

# Verify installation
pip list

# Run on wifi network for phone access

flask run --host=127.0.0.1 --port=5000

 * Running on all addresses (0.0.0.0)
 * Running on http://127.0.0.1:5000 // Desktop
 * Running on http://192.168.0.28:5000 // mobile
